EN: I worked overtime until late last night.

ZH: 他加班的时候总是很认真。
EN: He is always very diligent when working overtime.

ZH: 她加班是为了提升自己的职业发展。
EN: She works overtime to advance her career.

ZH: 加班并不一定是负面的体验。
EN: Overtime work is not necessarily a negative experience.

ZH: 下周我们需要加班来赶进度。
EN: We need to work overtime next week to catch up.

ZH: 加班是一种证明自己能力的方式。
EN: Overtime work is a way to prove one's abilities.

